      </p><p>
        If you wish, you can create one script that calls both the
        Service Manager and the Service Agent programs passing
        appropriate <code class="option">optionfile</code> options.
      </p></div><div class="section" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h3 class="title"><a name="mnmas-unattended-unix-osx"></a>3.7.3.Â Unattended Unix and Mac OS X Installation</h3></div></div></div><p>
