      </p><div class="section" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h4 class="title"><a name="functionality-1.2"></a>B.1.1.1.Â Functionality Added or Changed</h4></div></div></div><p>
          Agent:

          </p><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>
